laboratory_examinations.findings: Negative for Neisseria Gonorrhoeae by PCR.

Mild hypoventilatory changes at the dependent portions of the lung bases; No focal consolidation or effusion; Circular calcification in the inferior aspect of the cecum measuring 1.1 cm consistent with appendicoliths; Tubular rim enhancing structure distal measuring 1.8 cm fluid-filled with mild inflammatory changes; Focal cecal wall thickening noted; Small cyst within the left adnexa measuring 1.9 x 1.8 cm likely physiologic.
